{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I was here about four years ago,"},{"time":2000,"text":"talking about the relationship of design and happiness."},{"time":8000,"text":"At the very end of it, I showed a list under that title."},{"time":14000,"text":"I learned very few things in addition since"},{"time":20000,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":21000,"text":"but made a whole number of them into projects since."},{"time":27000,"text":"These are inflatable monkeys in every city in Scotland:"},{"time":32000,"text":"\"Everybody always thinks they are right.\""},{"time":40000,"text":"They were combined in the media."},{"time":45000,"text":"\"Drugs are fun in the beginning but become a drag later on.\""},{"time":55000,"text":"We're doing changing media."},{"time":59000,"text":"This is a projection that can see the viewer"},{"time":62000,"text":"as the viewer walks by."},{"time":64000,"text":"You can't help but actually ripping that spider web apart."},{"time":70000,"text":"All of these things are pieces of graphic design."},{"time":74000,"text":"We do them for our clients."},{"time":76000,"text":"They are commissioned."},{"time":78000,"text":"I would never have the money to actually pay for the installment"},{"time":82000,"text":"or pay for all the billboards or the production of these,"},{"time":87000,"text":"so there's always a client attached to them."},{"time":92000,"text":"These are 65,000 coat hangers in a street"},{"time":97000,"text":"that's lined with fashion stores."},{"time":103000,"text":"\"Worrying solves nothing.\""},{"time":105000,"text":"\"Money does not make me happy\""},{"time":111000,"text":"appeared first as double-page spreads in a magazine."},{"time":114000,"text":"The printer lost the file, didn't tell us."},{"time":117000,"text":"When the magazine -- actually, when I got the subscription --"},{"time":119000,"text":"it was 12 following pages."},{"time":121000,"text":"It said, \"Money does does make me happy.\""},{"time":124000,"text":"And a friend of mine in Austria felt so sorry for me"},{"time":130000,"text":"that he talked the largest casino owner in Linz"},{"time":135000,"text":"into letting us wrap his building."},{"time":138000,"text":"So this is the big pedestrian zone in Linz."},{"time":140000,"text":"It just says \"Money,\" and if you look down the side street,"},{"time":144000,"text":"it says, \"does not make me happy.\""},{"time":147000,"text":"We had a show that just came down last week in New York."},{"time":153000,"text":"We steamed up the windows permanently,"},{"time":155000,"text":"and every hour we had a different designer come in"},{"time":159000,"text":"and write these things that they've learned into the steam in the window."},{"time":163000,"text":"Everybody participated -- Milton Glaser,"},{"time":167000,"text":"Massimo Vignelli."},{"time":170000,"text":"Singapore was quite in discussion."},{"time":174000,"text":"This is a little spot that we filmed there"},{"time":179000,"text":"that's to be displayed on the large JumboTrons in Singapore."},{"time":185000,"text":"And, of course, it's one that's dear to my heart,"},{"time":190000,"text":"because all of these sentiments --"},{"time":192000,"text":"some banal, some a bit more profound --"},{"time":195000,"text":"all originally had come out of my diary."},{"time":211000,"text":"And I do go often into the diary"},{"time":213000,"text":"and check if I wanted to change something about the situation."},{"time":219000,"text":"If it's -- see it for a long enough time,"},{"time":221000,"text":"I actually do something about it."},{"time":225000,"text":"And the very last one is a billboard."},{"time":232000,"text":"This is our roof in New York, the roof of the studio."},{"time":236000,"text":"This is newsprint plus stencils that lie on the newsprint."},{"time":241000,"text":"We let that lie around in the sun."},{"time":242000,"text":"As you all know, newsprint yellows significantly in the sun."},{"time":247000,"text":"After a week, we took the stencils and the leaves off,"},{"time":249000,"text":"shipped the newsprints to Lisbon to a very sunny spot,"},{"time":254000,"text":"so on day one the billboard said,"},{"time":256000,"text":"\"Complaining is silly. Either act or forget.\""},{"time":259000,"text":"Three days later it faded, and a week later,"},{"time":262000,"text":"no more complaining anywhere."},{"time":265000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":266000,"text":"Thank you so much."},{"time":267000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}